Interface InferenceTest

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OnePropZTest, OneSampleTTest, TwoPropZTest, TwoSampleTTest

    public interface InferenceTest
    This interface contains methods universally needed to hypotehsis tests. The methods will be appropriately defined in each of 4 hypothesis test classes.
    Version:
    May 10, 2016
    Author:
    Durga Ganesh, Period: 3, Assignment: Statistics_Final, Sources: Power Team

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      double calculatePValue()
      This method will calculate the p value.
      double deviationOrError()
      This method will either calculate the standard deviation or the standard error based on the test.
      double testStatistic()
      This method will either calculate the z'score or t'statistic based on whether the data is categorical or quantitative.
